---
description: Product manager orchestration rules for clarifying scope, splitting work, and routing tasks across the skill repository.
alwaysApply: false
---

- Use this rule when a request needs requirement clarification, task breakdown, acceptance criteria, or cross-skill coordination.
- Clarify business goal, target user, scope, non-goals, and delivery phase first.
- Route design, frontend, mobile, backend, DBA, DevOps, comment, and commit work to the matching skill.
- Default to Chinese for requirement notes, acceptance criteria, comments guidance, and commit guidance unless explicitly changed.
